Package bto.EntitiesProjectRelated

package bto.EntitiesProjectRelated
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Enquiry
    The Enquiry class represents a question or request for information submitted by an applicant.
    FilterCriteria
    The FilterCriteria class provides a flexible way to define and apply filtering criteria for BTO housing entities like projects, applications, and bookings.
    FlatBooking
    The FlatBooking class represents a booking made by an applicant for a specific flat in a BTO project.
    OfficerRegistration
    The OfficerRegistration class represents a registration request from an HDB officer to work on a specific BTO project.
    Project
    The Project class represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project.
    ProjectApplication
    The ProjectApplication class represents an application submitted by an applicant for a BTO housing project.
    ProjectFlats
     
    Receipt
    The Receipt class represents a booking receipt for a BTO flat.
    Report
    Represents a report for flat bookings with configurable filtering and tracking.
    Withdrawal
    Represents a withdrawal request for a project application.
